    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2017 BMW M2 finished in striking Long Beach Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been adult-owned and garage-kept, serving as a cherished weekend driver. The exterior paint retains a deep, radiant luster, with only minor stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful road use. Inside, the carbon fiber trim and black Dakota leather upholstery are in excellent shape, showing minimal bolster wear on the driver\u2019s seat and a smoke-free environment. Mechanically, the car is superb; the 3.0L turbocharged inline-six delivers smooth, linear power, while the 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise, mechanical shifts. It features a complete service log, including a recent brake fluid flush and oil service. The car sits on factory wheels wrapped in Michelin Pilot Super Sport tires with significant tread depth remaining. This is a complete, turn-key performance coupe for a buyer who appreciates mechanical honesty and aesthetic pride.",
      "price": 36500.0,
